      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkRunner",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkRunner.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Executes a <xref href=\"Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkConfig\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> headlessly  -  without any UI  -  and\nproduces a <xref href=\"Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkSession\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> containing one\n<xref href=\"Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkResult\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> per configured router.</p>\n<p>\n<b>Threading:</b> designed to be called from <code>Task.Run</code> so that the\nBlazor UI thread stays responsive during the (potentially long) run.\nAll engine interaction happens through the singleton\n<xref href=\"Engine.Core.SimulationEngine.Instance\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> which is fully reset between runs.\n</p>\n<p>\n<b>Progress reporting:</b> the optional <code class=\"paramref\">onProgress</code>\ncallback in <xref href=\"Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkRunner.Run(Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkConfig%2cSystem.Collections.Generic.IReadOnlyDictionary%7bSystem.String%2cEngine.Routers.IPacketRouter%7d%2cSystem.Action%7bSystem.Int32%2cSystem.Int32%7d)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> is invoked after each completed router run\nwith <code>(routerIndex, totalRouters)</code> so callers can display a spinner.\n</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkSession.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkSession.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkSession",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkSession.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">The complete, serialisable record of one benchmark execution.\nStored as JSON so users can save, share, and reload results.</p>\n"
    },
    {
