      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Benchmark.DeviceBenchmarkDto",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Benchmark.DeviceBenchmarkDto.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Serialisable snapshot of a single device's configuration used inside\n<xref href=\"Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkConfig\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\nConverted to a live <xref href=\"Engine.Devices.Device\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> by\n<xref href=\"Engine.Benchmark.BenchmarkRunner\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> when it builds the engine state.\nDeclared as a <code>record</code> so Blazor event handlers can use <code>with</code>\nexpressions to create modified copies without mutating shared state.</p>\n"
    },
