      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Packets.ConfirmationPacket",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Packets.ConfirmationPacket.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A special packet that is automatically generated and sent back to the\noriginal sender when a packet with <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.NeedConfirmation\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nset to <code>true</code> is successfully delivered.\nThe payload contains the <xref href=\"System.Guid\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> bytes of the confirmed packet,\nallowing the sender to correlate the acknowledgement with the original\ntransmission.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.ControlPacket.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.ControlPacket.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Packets.ControlPacket",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Packets.ControlPacket.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A command packet sent from the <xref href=\"Engine.Devices.HubDevice\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to a specific\n<xref href=\"Engine.Devices.EmitterDevice\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to set its on/off state.</p>\n<p>\nThe hub generates <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.ControlPacket\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> instances automatically at\nthe interval configured on each <xref href=\"Engine.Devices.EmitterDevice\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> via\n<xref href=\"Engine.Devices.EmitterDevice.ControlFrequencyTicks\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\nWhen an <xref href=\"Engine.Devices.EmitterDevice\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> receives this packet it toggles its\n<xref href=\"Engine.Devices.EmitterDevice.State\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.ControlPacket.Command\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\n</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.Packet.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.Packet.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Packets.Packet",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Packets.Packet.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Represents a unit of data travelling through the simulation network.\nA packet knows its originator (<xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.From\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>), its intended\ndestination (<xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.To\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>), and the <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.NextHop\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> device it\nwill be delivered to on the next simulation tick.\nTravel time is expressed in engine ticks via <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.TicksToTravel\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>,\nand each hop decrements the <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.TTL\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> counter  -  a packet that\nreaches zero TTL is silently dropped.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.PacketData.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.PacketData.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Packets.PacketData",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Packets.PacketData.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Carries the application-level payload of a <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\nThe <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.PacketData.Data\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> property is intentionally untyped so that any\nvalue (sensor readings, command flags, raw bytes, etc.) can be transported\nwithout the engine imposing a schema.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.yml",
