      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A singleton that listens to <xref href=\"Engine.Core.SimulationEngine\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> events and\naccumulates simulation metrics.</p>\n<p>\nExtensibility: add a new <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.StatMetric\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.Metrics\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nand subscribe to any <xref href=\"Engine.Core.SimulationEngine\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> event to populate it.\nThe <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.Updated\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> event is raised after every change so UI layers\ncan re-render reactively without polling.\n</p>\n<p>\nEvery tick a <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.TickSnapshot\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> is appended to <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.History\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\n(capped at <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.MaxHistoryLength\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> entries) for time-series charts.\n</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Statistics.StatMetric.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Statistics.StatMetric.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Statistics.StatMetric",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Statistics.StatMetric.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A single observable metric tracked by <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\nUI layers bind to <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.StatMetric.DisplayValue\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> and listen to\n<xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.Updated\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> for re-renders.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Statistics.TickSnapshot.yml",
